lua-opengl
------------------------------------------
LuaGL provides access to all the OpenGL functionality from Lua.
Partial bindings for GLUT are also included.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.5.25-7
  libGL1-7.0.2-1
  libglut3-2.4.0-1
  lua-5.1.3-1

Build requirements:
  binutils-20060817-1
  cygport-0.3.8-1
  gcc-core-3.4.4-3
  make-3.81-1

Canonical website:
  http://luaforge.net/projects/

Canonical download:
  http://luaforge.net/projects/  

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack lua-opengl-1.01-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./lua-opengl-1.01-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/lua-opengl-1.01-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/lua-opengl-1.01-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

  /usr/lib/lua/5.1/glut.dll
  /usr/lib/lua/5.1/opengl.dll
  /usr/share/doc/lua-opengl-1.01/HISTORY.txt
  /usr/share/doc/lua-opengl-1.01/README.txt

------------------

Port Notes:

----- version 1.01-1 -----
Initial release for Cygwin.


